{"tid":2505984,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"木村有希傳下海拍AV 僅用貝殼遮胸拍寫真","createTime":"2021-04-27T04:35:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T13:47:30.000Z","uid":16659,"like":26,"dislike":90,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"deba761c72e98a4a8d838e730b1fa62c3c0d87d7","tid":2505984,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T04:35:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/SmRloR58lutmfEfwDGhqTZ5rULQ=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HIFAUJEXU5CO3I2K25DVVP6VRI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSmRloR58lutmfEfwDGhqTZ5rULQ%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHIFAUJEXU5CO3I2K25DVVP6VRI.jpg&h=729a201a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n24歲日本模特兒木村有希以火辣形象見稱，就近月來傳出負面消息，令她突然人氣下滑，還急急拍大膽寫真靠露肉救亡，下月25日便推出第三本個人寫真集《高興認識你》，全書共160頁，木村有希前往沖繩取景，以最性感一面示人，還標榜全部照片未經加工及沒有修圖，拍下多達3萬幅照片，今日再公開書中靚相，木村有希利用貝殼遮胸，據知她最初對今次拍攝構思半信半疑，但出來效果卻令她感到理想。<br />\n<br />\n木村有希去年在疫情期間急速增磅，立即被睇中成為纖體廣告代言人，於兩個月成功減約10磅。就在寫真集推出前夕，日本AV商Soft On Demand（SOD）旗下的「Super Star」啟動史上最大規模計劃，開價一億日圓（約709萬港元）邀請一位大卡士女星下海拍AV，由於這部新作是選用著名AV導演，總製作費高達二億日圓（約1,418萬港元），是非纏身的木村有希被指是嫌疑人物之一，但業界人士指下海女星其實是另有其人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tq2KT0jExSx3_tS1bIIzgUZI2dw=/802x1114/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3FT2NAPR3FHXXEHTU56YJRJHK4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ftq2KT0jExSx3_tS1bIIzgUZI2dw%3D%2F802x1114%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3FT2NAPR3FHXXEHTU56YJRJHK4.JPG&h=ae915b6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/a3W7HVBFSIaADR4iDIMRaCtWobU=/802x801/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/I24HAWXF2ZAWRNSBCPRXPWDIQ4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fa3W7HVBFSIaADR4iDIMRaCtWobU%3D%2F802x801%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FI24HAWXF2ZAWRNSBCPRXPWDIQ4.JPG&h=fee79a13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/etEeXzUTeT1qgMSmkQH8Rt4gb8M=/802x1208/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/W3NFV63SO5DZ3KAM3KK2EWCHZ4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FetEeXzUTeT1qgMSmkQH8Rt4gb8M%3D%2F802x1208%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FW3NFV63SO5DZ3KAM3KK2EWCHZ4.JPG&h=698dc8cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210427/FKOEOM2SQBF5FFEC67S55ORU2I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210427%2FFKOEOM2SQBF5FFEC67S55ORU2I%2F&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B609C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=b2cc8425\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210427%2FFKOEOM2SQBF5FFEC67S55ORU2I%2F&h=763ab1ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210427/FKOEOM2SQBF5FFEC67S55ORU2I/</a>"},{"pid":"17f6455ddb05b0520653d7049d50556c1ea8f1ed","tid":2505984,"uid":93096,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T04:35:33.000Z","msg":"正..？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cbf1e5b2574a8889db06119e0575ce2ed1cda74","tid":2505984,"uid":80047,"like":160,"dislike":5,"score":155,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T04:35:41.000Z","msg":"無波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92dd8c741e1869f478eca8cb392f58ee938917fd","tid":2505984,"uid":229026,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T04:37:14.000Z","msg":"會唔會太癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/p